{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6634c1b00","title":"井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会第一号决议──关于组织原则","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2f84fd9484","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":23,"articleId":"f6634c1b00","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"群众运动重要文献","id":"4bd6d6f93a","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"550a5d8a4b","name":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0122779c3c","type":"title","text":"井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会第一号决议──关于组织原则","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a33b174fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会第一号决议──关于组织原则","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9cdcd3c5bb","type":"paragraph","text":"清华大学井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a65ce92620","type":"paragraph","text":"1966.09.23","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9d97fc71ef","type":"paragraph","text":"我们井冈山红卫兵坚决贯彻党的阶级路线。井冈山红卫兵是以红五类为主体的革命的组织。第一，有成份论；第二，不唯成份论；第三，重在政治表现。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"59b22742f5","type":"paragraph","text":"什么样的人可以加入我们的组织？","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7551dddb9b","type":"paragraph","text":"基本条件：","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"de6e5b1bf0","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 他们是“敢”字当头，富有彻底的革命造反精神。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6d4d69bfb","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 他们必须要坚决地，全面地，不折不扣地贯彻十六条，努力学习毛泽东思想，照毛主席指示办事。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"697d80d224","type":"paragraph","text":"三、 他们必须用接班人五条标准时时刻刻要求自己。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b00b07852","type":"paragraph","text":"四、 他们必须要向解放军学习，坚决贯彻三八作风。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb1530df22","type":"paragraph","text":"五、 他们必须甘当群众小学生，善于听取群众意见。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9c471083c","type":"paragraph","text":"六、 他们必须富有自我批评精神，知错就改。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfc50678d3","type":"paragraph","text":"七、 他们必须是红五类子弟和一般出身的同志。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"eb8f74ef1f","type":"paragraph","text":"现在他们的基本观点必须是：","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7121cce80f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 认为临筹执行的是错误路线，并且敢造其反。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"483229409c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 认为毛泽东思想红卫兵总部犯了右倾错误。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c76ab41a78","type":"paragraph","text":"同意上述观点的非红五类子弟可加入井冈山战斗团。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"309738a287","type":"paragraph","text":"报名处：到二宿舍212领表填写。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e81285a5c","type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山红卫兵筹备建立委员会","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c2908cd4a2","type":"paragraph","text":"召集人：蒯大富、彭伟民、鲍长康","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"77babb2be7","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六六年九月二十三日","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f6634c1b00","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}